title: (Thurs Early) Bobby Is Going to Change A Show Member’s Life + Elder vs. Millennial + New Artist Gray Robinson and How Her Life Changed After Her BBS Debut
itunes:title: (Thurs Early) Bobby Is Going to Change A Show Member’s Life + Elder vs. Millennial + New Artist Gray Robinson and How Her Life Changed After Her BBS Debut
description:
Someone on the show’s life is going to change and they don’t even know it yet. Bobby reveals that there may be a new dream opportunity for someone on the show. Eddie and Morgan face off in a heated round of Elder vs. Millennial. New Artist Gray Robinson stops by to talk about getting a deal after being on our show for the first time, getting married since we saw her and performs a new song from her!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
